Explorer
========

The explorer plugin is a file/directory browser allowing the user to
open files with the internal editor or with the appropriate application
(Windows only).

![explorer](explorer.png)

Context menus may be used to run a script, open a terminal window or run
a Windows explorer window (Windows only):

![explorer_menu1](explorer_menu1.png)

![explorer_menu2](explorer_menu2.png)

